describe the moment--

00:08:08.320 --> 00:08:11.830 align:middle line:84%
sunk back into
what's-the-use-ness.

00:08:11.830 --> 00:08:14.720 align:middle line:90%


00:08:14.720 --> 00:08:18.760 align:middle line:84%
