was about to have the deepest

00:08:27.180 --> 00:08:28.975 align:middle line:90%
sleep of my life.

00:08:28.975 --> 00:08:33.696 align:middle line:84%
And instantly, I experienced
myself being

00:08:33.696 --> 00:08:36.190 align:middle line:90%
sucked off the bed.

00:08:36.190 --> 00:08:40.620 align:middle line:84%
I've described this to close
ones as the feeling that a fly

00:08:40.620 --> 00:08:45.010 align:middle line:84%
