some surface and managed to

00:08:45.010 --> 00:08:48.725 align:middle line:84%
get a vacuum cleaner hose over
that fly fast enough.

00:08:48.725 --> 00:08:51.323 align:middle line:84%
And they'd say, OK,
turn it on.

00:08:51.323 --> 00:08:52.680 align:middle line:90%
[SUCKING SOUND]

00:08:52.680 --> 00:08:56.160 align:middle line:84%
And that feeling fly must
have if that were to

00:08:56.160 --> 00:08:57.780 align:middle line:90%
happen was how I felt.

00:08:57.780 --> 00:09:02.090 align:middle line:84%
