00:09:07.576 --> 00:09:08.525 align:middle line:90%
And I looked strange.

00:09:08.525 --> 00:09:10.750 align:middle line:90%
I looked very strange.

00:09:10.750 --> 00:09:14.780 align:middle line:84%
And I knew instantly that
that was not me.

00:09:14.780 --> 00:09:17.480 align:middle line:90%
And I thought, oh, my.

00:09:17.480 --> 00:09:23.030 align:middle line:84%
I thought all this while
that I was that.

00:09:23.030 --> 00:09:26.020 align:middle line:84%
And I remember thinking,
but if I'm not

00:09:26.020 --> 00:09:28.710 align:middle line:90%
that, then who am I?

00:09:28.710 --> 00:09:33.520 align:middle line:90%


00:09:33.520 --> 00:09:36.960 align:middle line:84%
>>After you enter this place of
light, you have a panoramic

00:09:36.960 --> 00:09:38.080 align:middle line:90%
