opportunity of shedding the

00:10:12.740 --> 00:10:15.530 align:middle line:90%
karma from all of those lives.

00:10:15.530 --> 00:10:18.060 align:middle line:84%
The problem is that in the West,
we do not know how to

00:10:18.060 --> 00:10:19.540 align:middle line:90%
die consciously.

00:10:19.540 --> 00:10:22.980 align:middle line:84%
So we don't take up the
opportunity at that moment of

00:10:22.980 --> 00:10:27.400 align:middle line:84%
