momentum of those histories

00:10:27.400 --> 00:10:30.500 align:middle line:84%
and then bring them with us into
our next incarnation in

00:10:30.500 --> 00:10:31.920 align:middle line:90%
our next lifetime.

00:10:31.920 --> 00:10:34.510 align:middle line:84%
>>Anybody who thinks there's
not a life after death is

00:10:34.510 --> 00:10:37.110 align:middle line:90%
stupid, end of story.

00:10:37.110 --> 00:10:40.480 align:middle line:84%
I've been through three
