00:11:40.860 --> 00:11:42.110 align:middle line:90%
17.

00:11:42.110 --> 00:11:45.460 align:middle line:90%


00:11:45.460 --> 00:11:47.010 align:middle line:90%
I began to see things.

00:11:47.010 --> 00:11:50.060 align:middle line:84%
But then I didn't think
much of it.

00:11:50.060 --> 00:11:54.675 align:middle line:84%
>>Before we have a dream, we go
through sleeping process,

00:11:54.675 --> 00:11:57.640 align:middle line:90%
deep sleep process.

00:11:57.640 --> 00:12:03.768 align:middle line:84%
That in itself is a very good
practice of rehearsal,

00:12:03.768 --> 00:12:08.500 align:middle line:84%
practice of dying, death
and dying process.

00:12:08.500 --> 00:12:12.720 align:middle line:84%
The way we sleep, when we sleep
and lie down, how our

00:12:12.720 --> 00:12:19.240 align:middle line:84%
consciousness withdraws
inwardly, how our experiences

00:12:19.240 --> 00:12:25.620 align:middle line:84%
of perceptions and thoughts
become dreamlike in fading and

00:12:25.620 --> 00:12:29.140 align:middle line:84%
then slowly, slowly, sinking
inwardly into the base

00:12:29.140 --> 00:12:30.160 align:middle line:90%
consciousness--

00:12:30.160 --> 00:12:35.390 align:middle line:90%
and then we go blank.

00:12:35.390 --> 00:12:42.060 align:middle line:84%
>>And so I left and went
to London from V-Day.

00:12:42.060 --> 00:12:43.560 align:middle line:90%
I shouldn't have just left.

00:12:43.560 --> 00:12:46.950 align:middle line:84%
I just went, took the bus,
and went to London.

00:12:46.950 --> 00:12:50.210 align:middle line:84%
And I got there on the day when
victory was declared.

00:12:50.210 --> 00:12:54.980 align:middle line:84%
And all of the cars were
hooting and tooting.

00:12:54.980 --> 00:12:59.050 align:middle line:84%
I went into that little tiny
restaurant, which was a hole

00:12:59.050 --> 00:13:01.565 align:middle line:90%
in the wall, in Swiss Cottage.

00:13:01.565 --> 00:13:03.010 align:middle line:90%
You know London?

00:13:03.010 --> 00:13:03.700 align:middle line:90%
OK.

00:13:03.700 --> 00:13:06.660 align:middle line:84%
And I went right in there and
the tables were all empty.

00:13:06.660 --> 00:13:07.680 align:middle line:84%
There must have been
six tables.

00:13:07.680 --> 00:13:09.310 align:middle line:90%
It was a small place.

00:13:09.310 --> 00:13:13.280 align:middle line:84%
I sat down at one of the empty
tables in my uniform.

00:13:13.280 --> 00:13:18.630 align:middle line:84%
And in walked this tall man
who was very pale who was

00:13:18.630 --> 00:13:23.690 align:middle line:84%
wearing a blue Air Force
officer's uniform.

00:13:23.690 --> 00:13:27.070 align:middle line:84%
And he sat down at my table
and with all the

00:13:27.070 --> 00:13:28.840 align:middle line:90%
empties all around me.

00:13:28.840 --> 00:13:31.830 align:middle line:90%
And he said, hello, Renate.

00:13:31.830 --> 00:13:33.160 align:middle line:90%
And I said, hello.

00:13:33.160 --> 00:13:34.570 align:middle line:90%
How do you know my name?

00:13:34.570 --> 00:13:36.940 align:middle line:84%
He said, I know everything
about you.

00:13:36.940 --> 00:13:38.900 align:middle line:90%
I said, really?

00:13:38.900 --> 00:13:40.410 align:middle line:84%
And I was trying
to be adorable.

00:13:40.410 --> 00:13:41.390 align:middle line:90%
I said, is it good?

00:13:41.390 --> 00:13:43.770 align:middle line:90%
Is it bad?

00:13:43.770 --> 00:13:45.370 align:middle line:90%
It was all of 20.

00:13:45.370 --> 00:13:49.660 align:middle line:84%
And he said, I came as
a message for you.

00:13:49.660 --> 00:13:51.180 align:middle line:90%
It sounds like television.

00:13:51.180 --> 00:13:54.230 align:middle line:90%
But I said, what is it?

00:13:54.230 --> 00:13:58.590 align:middle line:84%
And he said, your whole
family is dead.

00:13:58.590 --> 00:13:59.310 align:middle line:90%
They're all dead.

00:13:59.310 --> 00:13:59.850 align:middle line:90%
Your mother's dead.

00:13:59.850 --> 00:14:01.640 align:middle line:90%
Your father's dead.

00:14:01.640 --> 00:14:04.130 align:middle line:84%
Everybody's dead except
your sister and you.

00:14:04.130 --> 00:14:07.080 align:middle line:84%
>>I believe that the soul
incarnates in the body for the

00:14:07.080 --> 00:14:08.390 align:middle line:84%
lessons that we need
to learn here.

00:14:08.390 --> 00:14:09.940 align:middle line:90%
And I think it is choice.

00:14:09.940 --> 00:14:11.650 align:middle line:84%
And I don't know if there's
timeline-- if you can come

00:14:11.650 --> 00:14:13.750 align:middle line:84%
right back or if there's
a wait period.

00:14:13.750 --> 00:14:18.060 align:middle line:84%
Many people say to me, John, how
do I know that when I pass

00:14:18.060 --> 00:14:19.240 align:middle line:84%
away, my mother's going
to be there?

00:14:19.240 --> 00:14:21.200 align:middle line:90%
She didn't reincarnate.

00:14:21.200 --> 00:14:23.830 align:middle line:84%
Well, I learned an analogy
from another medium.

00:14:23.830 --> 00:14:25.030 align:middle line:90%
Look at it this way.

00:14:25.030 --> 00:14:26.800 align:middle line:90%
You have a hard drive.

00:14:26.800 --> 00:14:28.200 align:middle line:90%
That's your oversoul.

00:14:28.200 --> 00:14:30.810 align:middle line:84%
And that John Holland program
spits out and is

00:14:30.810 --> 00:14:32.460 align:middle line:90%
playing right now.

00:14:32.460 --> 00:14:35.910 align:middle line:84%
So when I pass away, when I
leave this body, that John

00:14:35.910 --> 00:14:38.770 align:middle line:84%
Holland program ceases to play
and goes back into the

00:14:38.770 --> 00:14:41.230 align:middle line:84%
database, goes back into
the hard drive.

00:14:41.230 --> 00:14:43.000 align:middle line:84%
Another piece of my soul
will come down.

00:14:43.000 --> 00:14:46.900 align:middle line:84%
But that piece of that John
Holland program will always be

00:14:46.900 --> 00:14:49.040 align:middle line:90%
there in the database.

00:14:49.040 --> 00:14:51.680 align:middle line:84%
So I think we come back just for
our soul progression, to

00:14:51.680 --> 00:14:56.010 align:middle line:84%
keep learning lessons, because
this is the place to do it.

00:14:56.010 --> 00:14:58.340 align:middle line:90%
But sometimes--

00:14:58.340 --> 00:15:00.450 align:middle line:84%
and I often joke and say, I
think the people on the other

00:15:00.450 --> 00:15:01.760 align:middle line:84%
side, when I say,
you know what?

00:15:01.760 --> 00:15:03.430 align:middle line:84%
I want to go back to Earth
and learn more lessons.

00:15:03.430 --> 00:15:05.640 align:middle line:84%
I think sometimes, the people
on the other side say, why?

00:15:05.640 --> 00:15:08.300 align:middle line:90%
So this is life.

00:15:08.300 --> 00:15:09.210 align:middle line:90%
This is the school of life.

00:15:09.210 --> 00:15:10.200 align:middle line:84%
And this is where you learn
all your lessons.

00:15:10.200 --> 00:15:13.160 align:middle line:84%
And what better place for the
soul to learn than being this

00:15:13.160 --> 00:15:15.730 align:middle line:84%
dense, molecular-- it's
tough being in here.

00:15:15.730 --> 00:15:17.870 align:middle line:84%
So this is where we
learn our lessons.

00:15:17.870 --> 00:15:22.680 align:middle line:84%
And when we leave the spirit
world, I think they say

00:15:22.680 --> 00:15:24.730 align:middle line:84%
goodbye to us, but they
say hello to us here.

00:15:24.730 --> 00:15:27.320 align:middle line:84%
And then when it's time for us
to pass, the people here

00:15:27.320 --> 00:15:30.300 align:middle line:84%
mourn, and those on the other
side, they celebrate and say

00:15:30.300 --> 00:15:31.320 align:middle line:90%
welcome back.

00:15:31.320 --> 00:15:35.530 align:middle line:84%
>>And then they showed
me who I had been.

00:15:35.530 --> 00:15:40.460 align:middle line:84%
They took me through former
lifetimes, through a past life

00:15:40.460 --> 00:15:44.200 align:middle line:84%
regression in which I was
there personally,

00:15:44.200 --> 00:15:46.500 align:middle line:90%
feeling it, living it.

00:15:46.500 --> 00:15:48.930 align:middle line:84%
I was in the desert feeling
the desert sand

00:15:48.930 --> 00:15:50.810 align:middle line:90%
blowing in my face.

00:15:50.810 --> 00:15:53.590 align:middle line:84%
I was in the jungle feeling
the sweat in my body.

00:15:53.590 --> 00:15:55.790 align:middle line:90%
I was a woman giving birth.

00:15:55.790 --> 00:15:57.960 align:middle line:90%
I was drowning in the ocean.

00:15:57.960 --> 00:16:00.250 align:middle line:90%
I was being killed in battle.

00:16:00.250 --> 00:16:02.980 align:middle line:84%
I was being taken
away as a child.

00:16:02.980 --> 00:16:05.020 align:middle line:84%
And I asked them, who
are these people?

00:16:05.020 --> 00:16:07.550 align:middle line:84%
And they said, they have
also been you.

00:16:07.550 --> 00:16:10.170 align:middle line:84%
But you're not any
of them, either.

00:16:10.170 --> 00:16:12.410 align:middle line:84%
They're just the experiences
you've had.

00:16:12.410 --> 00:16:14.540 align:middle line:84%
>>I was pulled out
of the room.

00:16:14.540 --> 00:16:19.386 align:middle line:84%
And I flew out of that
room like lightning.

00:16:19.386 --> 00:16:24.760 align:middle line:84%
And I was, in fact, in a tunnel,
in fact, racing toward

00:16:24.760 --> 00:16:27.210 align:middle line:84%
a light at the end
of this tunnel.

00:16:27.210 --> 00:16:30.280 align:middle line:84%
And I was going at some
insane speed.

00:16:30.280 --> 00:16:33.540 align:middle line:84%
Things were flying by me-- just
the shadows and the light

00:16:33.540 --> 00:16:36.560 align:middle line:84%
flowing in this tunnel, so fast
I knew I must be going a

00:16:36.560 --> 00:16:39.260 align:middle line:90%
gazillion miles an hour.

00:16:39.260 --> 00:16:42.940 align:middle line:84%
And finally, I came out at the
end of this tunnel-like

00:16:42.940 --> 00:16:45.600 align:middle line:84%
environment, and I found
myself in the

00:16:45.600 --> 00:16:47.455 align:middle line:90%
presence of this light.

00:16:47.455 --> 00:16:50.570 align:middle line:90%


00:16:50.570 --> 00:16:54.180 align:middle line:84%
It wasn't a point of light
existing in a field of

00:16:54.180 --> 00:16:55.330 align:middle line:90%
relative darkness.

00:16:55.330 --> 00:16:58.830 align:middle line:84%
It was expansive light that
existed everywhere.

00:16:58.830 --> 00:17:01.070 align:middle line:84%
But it seemed to be brighter
and hotter in the direct

00:17:01.070 --> 00:17:02.725 align:middle line:84%
center, although it
was everywhere.

00:17:02.725 --> 00:17:05.410 align:middle line:90%


00:17:05.410 --> 00:17:09.190 align:middle line:84%
I could feel warmth, but not
warmth in the physical sense--

00:17:09.190 --> 00:17:12.430 align:middle line:84%
just a warmth the way when you
feel warmly towards someone--

00:17:12.430 --> 00:17:15.096 align:middle line:84%
that kind of warmth,
emotional warmth.

00:17:15.096 --> 00:17:19.050 align:middle line:84%
I could feel enormous
emotional warmth and

00:17:19.050 --> 00:17:26.030 align:middle line:90%
incredible peace.

00:17:26.030 --> 00:17:29.133 align:middle line:84%
>>This life review is the
greatest teaching tool that

00:17:29.133 --> 00:17:31.140 align:middle line:84%
you will ever have to understand
the meaning of

00:17:31.140 --> 00:17:33.896 align:middle line:84%
life, the purpose and the
direction that you're going in

00:17:33.896 --> 00:17:35.810 align:middle line:90%
and what it's all about.

00:17:35.810 --> 00:17:38.000 align:middle line:84%
After the panoramic life
review, the system

00:17:38.000 --> 00:17:40.980 align:middle line:90%
of judgment is this.

00:17:40.980 --> 00:17:44.890 align:middle line:84%
If the Holy Spirit could not
come today and it sent you, in

00:17:44.890 --> 00:17:48.020 align:middle line:84%
the life you just reviewed, what
difference did it make?

00:17:48.020 --> 00:17:50.715 align:middle line:84%
And that's when you see the
value of your spiritual

00:17:50.715 --> 00:17:53.960 align:middle line:84%
identity, the great power and
greatness about yourself.

00:17:53.960 --> 00:17:56.450 align:middle line:90%
And then that passes.

00:17:56.450 --> 00:17:58.175 align:middle line:84%
And then you're back,
just you.

00:17:58.175 --> 00:18:00.170 align:middle line:90%
I wasn't Dannion after that.

00:18:00.170 --> 00:18:03.630 align:middle line:84%
I was that divine spiritual,
playful being with dignity,

00:18:03.630 --> 00:18:05.220 align:middle line:90%
direction, and purpose.

00:18:05.220 --> 00:18:07.310 align:middle line:84%
>>And then they showed
me the future.

00:18:07.310 --> 00:18:10.160 align:middle line:84%
They showed me what I
came here to do--

00:18:10.160 --> 00:18:14.920 align:middle line:84%
that I came here to serve, to do
my little bit to be able to

00:18:14.920 --> 00:18:18.120 align:middle line:84%
help humanity, to assist others,
to be compassionate,

00:18:18.120 --> 00:18:20.060 align:middle line:90%
to be caring.

00:18:20.060 --> 00:18:22.240 align:middle line:84%
And they said, if you leave now,
you will miss that great

00:18:22.240 --> 00:18:23.610 align:middle line:90%
opportunity.

00:18:23.610 --> 00:18:24.810 align:middle line:90%
>>And I said, who killed them?

00:18:24.810 --> 00:18:27.570 align:middle line:84%
He said, the Nazis killed
them in camps.

00:18:27.570 --> 00:18:30.082 align:middle line:84%
And some of them, they
burned on the train.

00:18:30.082 --> 00:18:31.750 align:middle line:90%
I said, really?

00:18:31.750 --> 00:18:32.750 align:middle line:90%
All of them?

00:18:32.750 --> 00:18:34.090 align:middle line:90%
All of them.

00:18:34.090 --> 00:18:36.650 align:middle line:84%
And then it struck me there
was something wrong.

00:18:36.650 --> 00:18:38.645 align:middle line:90%
I said, what are you?

00:18:38.645 --> 00:18:40.090 align:middle line:90%
How can you know that?

00:18:40.090 --> 00:18:44.440 align:middle line:84%
He said, I'm a heavenly
social worker.

00:18:44.440 --> 00:18:47.040 align:middle line:84%
I said, a heavenly
social worker?

00:18:47.040 --> 00:18:48.290 align:middle line:90%
They have that?

00:18:48.290 --> 00:18:50.040 align:middle line:90%
And he said, yes.

00:18:50.040 --> 00:18:51.685 align:middle line:84%
I said, are those
guardian angels?

00:18:51.685 --> 00:18:53.220 align:middle line:90%
He said, yes.

00:18:53.220 --> 00:18:58.520 align:middle line:84%
Sort of a lesser angel that
takes care of the humans.

00:18:58.520 --> 00:19:00.240 align:middle line:90%
I said, and you know me?

00:19:00.240 --> 00:19:04.210 align:middle line:84%
He said, for many,
many centuries.

00:19:04.210 --> 00:19:06.160 align:middle line:90%
I said, really?

00:19:06.160 --> 00:19:10.590 align:middle line:84%
I said, so how come they killed
all of the family?

00:19:10.590 --> 00:19:11.980 align:middle line:84%
He said, they killed
all the Jews.

00:19:11.980 --> 00:19:15.600 align:middle line:84%
You see, where I was in London,
we never heard about

00:19:15.600 --> 00:19:16.830 align:middle line:90%
the Holocaust.

00:19:16.830 --> 00:19:19.336 align:middle line:90%
And we never anything.

00:19:19.336 --> 00:19:21.630 align:middle line:90%
It was secret.

00:19:21.630 --> 00:19:25.992 align:middle line:84%
>>I was in the presence of
this extraordinary light.

00:19:25.992 --> 00:19:35.620 align:middle line:84%
And I remember feeling ashamed,
suddenly, and

00:19:35.620 --> 00:19:37.960 align:middle line:90%
embarrassed.

00:19:37.960 --> 00:19:41.650 align:middle line:84%
Mind you, I was very clear in my
sense of things-- that the

00:19:41.650 --> 00:19:44.350 align:middle line:84%
shame and the embarrassment
was not coming

00:19:44.350 --> 00:19:45.440 align:middle line:90%
from another place.

00:19:45.440 --> 00:19:48.340 align:middle line:90%
I didn't feel judged.

00:19:48.340 --> 00:19:55.450 align:middle line:84%
What I felt was how you might
feel if the Queen of England

00:19:55.450 --> 00:20:00.970 align:middle line:84%
came to your door unexpectedly
and the house was a mess, and

00:20:00.970 --> 00:20:03.440 align:middle line:84%
you normally have it pretty
clean, but that moment wasn't

00:20:03.440 --> 00:20:04.250 align:middle line:90%
one of those moments.

00:20:04.250 --> 00:20:06.290 align:middle line:90%
And in she came flouncing in.

00:20:06.290 --> 00:20:08.520 align:middle line:84%
And you just-- she had no
judgment about it, but she

00:20:08.520 --> 00:20:10.130 align:middle line:84%
still is, after all, the
Queen of England.

00:20:10.130 --> 00:20:12.540 align:middle line:84%
And the house looks
like a mess.

00:20:12.540 --> 00:20:15.670 align:middle line:84%
>>And so, I said, they
killed everybody?

00:20:15.670 --> 00:20:18.980 align:middle line:90%
He said, pretty much.

00:20:18.980 --> 00:20:19.640 align:middle line:90%
I was so shocked.

00:20:19.640 --> 00:20:21.570 align:middle line:84%
I still see myself
sitting there.

00:20:21.570 --> 00:20:23.480 align:middle line:84%
He said, I'm going to spend
some time with you.

00:20:23.480 --> 00:20:26.360 align:middle line:90%
I spent three days with him.

00:20:26.360 --> 00:20:29.210 align:middle line:84%
>>At night, I would go to
this hostel where they

00:20:29.210 --> 00:20:30.060 align:middle line:90%
had a bed for me.

00:20:30.060 --> 00:20:31.880 align:middle line:84%
I went asking if I
could sleep over.

00:20:31.880 --> 00:20:33.290 align:middle line:90%
They said, yes.

00:20:33.290 --> 00:20:35.560 align:middle line:84%
And then I said his
name was John.

00:20:35.560 --> 00:20:36.750 align:middle line:90%
And I said, what's your name?

00:20:36.750 --> 00:20:38.660 align:middle line:90%
He said, John.

00:20:38.660 --> 00:20:39.610 align:middle line:90%
He was very pale.

00:20:39.610 --> 00:20:41.550 align:middle line:90%
And he had very blue eyes.

00:20:41.550 --> 00:20:48.120 align:middle line:84%
And I said, so let me
ask you things.

00:20:48.120 --> 00:20:48.970 align:middle line:90%
He said, all right.

00:20:48.970 --> 00:20:52.640 align:middle line:90%
Are you Jewish, I said.

00:20:52.640 --> 00:20:54.220 align:middle line:90%
He said, no.

00:20:54.220 --> 00:20:55.330 align:middle line:90%
I said, are you Christian?

00:20:55.330 --> 00:20:56.980 align:middle line:90%
He said, no.

00:20:56.980 --> 00:20:58.620 align:middle line:90%
I said, so what are you?

00:20:58.620 --> 00:21:01.550 align:middle line:84%
And he said, we have a different
form of worship.

00:21:01.550 --> 00:21:02.710 align:middle line:90%
I said, is there a god?

00:21:02.710 --> 00:21:04.250 align:middle line:90%
He said, yes.

00:21:04.250 --> 00:21:05.380 align:middle line:90%
What does it look like?

00:21:05.380 --> 00:21:07.030 align:middle line:90%
He said, it doesn't look like.

00:21:07.030 --> 00:21:10.030 align:middle line:84%
You're sitting in the
middle of it.

00:21:10.030 --> 00:21:11.430 align:middle line:90%
I remember that.

00:21:11.430 --> 00:21:14.920 align:middle line:84%
I said, well, why does
he allow that?

00:21:14.920 --> 00:21:19.630 align:middle line:84%
He said, men bring this
on themselves.

00:21:19.630 --> 00:21:21.250 align:middle line:90%
Everything is free choice.

00:21:21.250 --> 00:21:25.210 align:middle line:84%
I said, my people
wanted to die?

00:21:25.210 --> 00:21:29.990 align:middle line:84%
Yes, he said, probably, because
this is how much karma

00:21:29.990 --> 00:21:31.760 align:middle line:90%
got removed.

00:21:31.760 --> 00:21:35.840 align:middle line:84%
That was, the people in the camp
had their karma removed.

00:21:35.840 --> 00:21:39.646 align:middle line:84%
It was like a bonus
or something.

00:21:39.646 --> 00:21:41.558 align:middle line:90%
Really?, I said.

00:21:41.558 --> 00:21:43.470 align:middle line:90%
Ah.

00:21:43.470 --> 00:21:48.260 align:middle line:84%
So you mean there is choice
about-- everything is choice.

00:21:48.260 --> 00:21:50.930 align:middle line:84%
What about the evil
ones like Hitler?

